."}, {"version": "omega-ruby", "text": "Snorunt live in regions with heavy snowfall. In seasons without snow, such as spring and summer, this Pok\u00e9mon steals away to live quietly among stalactites and stalagmites deep in caverns."}, {"version": "pearl", "text": "In the snow country, certain folklore says a house will prosper if a SNORUNT lives there."}, {"version": "platinum", "text": "It is said that several SNORUNT gather under giant leaves and live together in harmony."}, {"version": "ruby", "text": "SNORUNT live in regions with heavy snowfall. In seasons without snow, such as spring and summer, this POK\u00e9MON steals away to live quietly among stalactites and stalagmites deep in caverns."}, {"version": "sapphire", "text": "SNORUNT survives by eating only snow and ice. Old folklore claims that a house visited by this POK\u00e9MON is sure to prosper for many generations to come."}, {"version": "shield", "text": "It can only survive in cold areas. It bounces happily around, even in environments as cold as \u2212150 degrees Fahrenheit."}, {"version": "soulsilver", "text": "It\u2019s said that if they are seen at midnight, they\u2019ll cause heavy snow. They eat snow and ice to survive."}, {"version": "sun", "text": "Their numbers seem to have rapidly increased in Alola. Custom has it that houses where Snorunt live will be prosperous for generations to come."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "It\u2019s said that if they are seen at midnight, they\u2019ll cause heavy snow. They eat snow and ice to survive."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "Rich people from cold areas all share childhood memories of playing with Snorunt."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "It feeds mainly on ice and snow. It\u2019s only able to survive in a limited number of places in the warm Alola region."}, {"version": "white", "text": "It is said that several Snorunt gather under giant leaves and live together in harmony."}, {"version": "white-2", "text": "It is said that several Snorunt g